title: Bezos Picks New CEO for Space Company as SpaceX Dominates Industry
description: Dave Limp, who worked on several major products at Amazon.com, will take over for the current Blue Origin CEO, Bob Smith.

title: ChatGPT Can Now Chat Aloud With You (And Yes, It Sounds Pretty Much Human)
description: OpenAI’s popular chatbot is speaking up—literally—with a selection of voices that sound eerily like a real human. Plus, you can now upload photos and the chatbot can interpret them.

title: Amazon to Invest Up to $4 Billion in Anthropic as AI Arms Race Escalates
description: The deal, which includes a broad partnership, follows Microsoft’s multibillion-dollar stake in rival startup OpenAI.

title: Want to Sell on TikTok? For Many Chinese Merchants, It Isn't So Simple.
description: Picking the right product, avoiding cultural faux pas and navigating social media are all part of challenges even experienced exporters face.
